<Font|headerFont>TELEPORT DISPLAY<Font|helpFont><p><p>

Use the Teleport display to transport yourself quickly from one station to another or to
board a ship as a turret gunner.<p><p>

<Font|smallBoldFont>To access the Teleport display<Font|helpFont><p><p>

<Bullet|hlpbullet|In the hangar, click the Teleport location, or press F8.><p><p>

<Font|subheaderFont>TELEPORTING BETWEEN STATIONS<Font|helpFont><p><p>

All stations have teleportation capability. Teleporting yourself, or ripcording, to another
station before launching is a good way to get close to the action quickly. For immediate
access to hotspots or to mining operations, or simply to establish a staging area for assaults
on the enemy, building Teleportation Receivers is a worthy investment.<p><p>

<Font|smallBoldFont>To teleport to any station or Transportation Receiver<Font|helpFont><p><p>

<Bullet|hlpbullet|In the Teleport display, click the station you want to
transport to, and then click <Font|smallBoldFont>Transfer/Board.<Font|helpFont>><p><p>

<Bullet|hlpblank|-or-><p><p>

<Bullet|hlpblank|In flight, press and hold the R key until you are
transferred to the nearest station or Teleportation Receiver.><p><p>

<Bullet|hlpblank|When you press and hold R, a countdown begins and
all sectors that you can teleport to appear with a red border
around them in the Map display. The sector you will teleport to has a
thicker border. To change the sector you will teleport to, click that sector while
holding down the R key. The countdown will begin again.><p><p>

Note that interceptors, frigates, and miners and constructors do not have
the ability to use Teleportation Receivers.<p><p>

<Font|subheaderFont>BECOMING A TURRET GUNNER<Font|helpFont><p><p>

Playing as a turret gunner in the bomber or in a capital ship is an
excellent way for a new Allegiance player to learn the game. For details
on the role of the turret gunner, access Quick Reference: <Main|hlpe2b2|The Turret Gunner><p><p>

<Font|smallBoldFont>To become a turret gunner<Font|helpFont><p><p>

<Bullet|hlpbullet|In the Teleport display, click a ship that has a
turret opening, and then click <Font|smallBoldFont>Transfer/Board.<Font|helpFont>><p><p>

<Font|smallBoldFont>To remove yourself from a ship as a turret gunner<Font|helpFont><p><p>

<Bullet|hlpbullet|In the Teleport display, click a station, and then
click <Font|smallBoldFont>Transfer/Board.<Font|helpFont>><p><p>

<Bullet|hlpblank|-or-><p><p>

<Bullet|hlpblank|In the Loadout screen, click a ship you want to
pilot, and then click <Font|smallBoldFont>Confirm Change.<Font|helpFont>><p><p>

<Bullet|hlpblank|-or-><p><p>

<Bullet|hlpblank|In flight, press CTRL+SHIFT+D, D, D to escape in an
eject pod.>